es/705634/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/705634/answer",,,,,"17","Health","Health","2017-02-27","Epilepsy: Children","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health, what the average waiting time is for children seeking access to the ketogenic diet for the treatment of epilepsy.","false","Biography information for Catherine West","Hornsey and Wood Green","Catherine West","65605"
