"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/705788","Department for Exiting the European Union","false","2017-03-06","<p>The Department for Exiting the European Union was created in July 2016. Information relating to the Department’s expenditure in 2016-17 will be published in the Annual Report in July 2017.</p><p> </p>","Worcester","Mr Robin Walker",,"2017-03-06T14:36:09.617Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/705788/answer","Biography information for Mr Robin Walker","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/705788/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/705788/answer",,,,,"203","Exiting the European Union","Exiting the European Union","2017-02-27","Department for Exiting the European Union: Procurement","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Exiting the European Union, what the procurement spend of his Department was in each year since 2010.","false","Biography information for Jon Trickett","Hemsworth","Jon Trickett","65684"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/705789","Department for Exiting the European Union","false","2017-03-02","<p>The department continues to discuss with Sir Mark Walport, the Government's Chief Scientific Adviser, what more we should do to ensure that DExEU is accessing the very best scientific expertise.</p><p>There are several models for achieving this, and it is important for us to take into account DExEU’s role as a co-ordinating department when considering what provisions to put in place.</p><p>The department is currently exploring these options, including considering the appointment of a Chief Scientific Adviser.<strong><br></strong></p>","Worcester","Mr Robin Walker",,"2017-03-02T16:23:18.19Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/705789/answer","Biography information for Mr Robin Walker","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/705789/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/705789/answer",,,,,"203","Exiting the European Union","Exiting the European Union","2017-02-27","Government Chief Scientific Adviser","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Exiting the European Union, if he plans to appoint a Chief Science Adviser prior to the opening of the negotiations on the UK leaving the EU.","false","Biography information for Dan Jarvis","Barnsley Central","Dan Jarvis","65659"
